room_title: Escape room "Bomb Squad" by TrappedKC in Kansas City
room_address: 618 SW 3rd St, Ste E Lee's Summit, MO 64063
room_description: You and your group are part of an elite bomb-solving team. You have gotten intel that reveals that a bomb has been planted in a local Motel. Problem is, the area can't be evacuated - so it's all up to you. Lives are on the line, can you defuse the bomb?
